Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's dance magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.66,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Once you have it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:10.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Let your body move,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:09.95,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Those girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Step into the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's dance magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.17,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And it's electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:19.23,Juniper,,0,0,0,,First, they get me kicked off the Daring Do set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.30,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Now…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.47,Juniper,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:27.80,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I bet they'll be at the premiere tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:31.79,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I bet I'll be the lucky one ushering them to their seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.67,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Juniper, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:41.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We need you back at the popcorn popper stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:43.53,Juniper,,0,0,0,,What was that…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:45.23,Juniper,,0,0,0,,boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:46.62,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:49.28,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Losing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:54.12,Juniper,,0,0,0,,If those girls hadn't shown up, I would have played Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:55.85,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Tonight would have been about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.90,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I would have been a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:03.95,Juniper,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.56,Juniper,,0,0,0,,They are a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:18.74,Juniper,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.15,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.19,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Keep the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:36.57,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Something tells me this thing's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:02.21,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Dear Princess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.82,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,tonight's the night of the big movie premiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:08.15,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,All my friends are really excited, and I should be too, except…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.74,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to keep my mind on anything other than our new powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.89,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,and the rogue magic that's loose in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.12,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,and how scary but exhilarating it all is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:20.42,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,How does it work? How can we be prepared for it?\NWhen will it show up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.48,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, you see the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:27.78,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,With the weight of all Equestria on your shoulders, you must have some advice on how to…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.23,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.65,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:32.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sunset Shimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.35,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just… ran out of pages in my journal. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Chillax, SunShim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Who's "SunShim"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's Sunset Shimmer's new movie star name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I just made it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:51.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,For sweet apples' sake, we only have bit parts in this flick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We're not movie stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yet, darling. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:59.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's more bothering you than just journal pages, isn't there, Sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Share your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It might help soothe your stressed nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna take any of the fun out of our big night…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:11.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I said spill it, SunShim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:12.84,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.14,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's just that things have been calm around here, magic-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And that's bad how, precisely?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:19.90,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:23.10,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's just that instead of enjoying the fact that things are calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:26.71,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm constantly thinking about things going wrong, even when they aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Like… like what things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.63,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.34,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't even be thinking about any of this stuff right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.27,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,And neither should any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Look! Twilight's writing you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:40.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, Sunset's getting an Equestritext!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.04,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight wants me to come to…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.29,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:55.78,Juniper,,0,0,0,,It's like this mirror is the only one around here who gets me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.47,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,Popcorn spill at the condiment counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.03,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Does this look like someone who cleans popcorn spills?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.00,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.31,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,It looks like someone about to fire somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.57,Juniper,,0,0,0,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.62,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know what will perk me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.49,Juniper,,0,0,0,,A little Mirror Me time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.63,Juniper,,0,0,0,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:33.97,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wish this popcorn would just clean itself up so I could just stare at you all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:41.45,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,Whuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:42.77,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,Done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:43.41,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.75,SomeponyLightCyan,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.42,Juniper,,0,0,0,,You and me both!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.63,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:20.69,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.04,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.90,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,That feels a little weird after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.86,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.67,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You're Twilight's student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.67,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.19,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She wanted me to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She wanted to give it to you herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:04.10,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but then she and her friends were called away to solve a friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That happens a lot around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.94,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,That must be stressful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.61,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Never knowing when you might be called on to save the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.98,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Dropping everything at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.82,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,How does she do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry. She just told me to give you the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.60,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,So, are you sure she won't be back anytime soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:27.95,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.23,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,O… kay… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.85,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,guess I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.07,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What's it like back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.84,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's pretty different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.51,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,And not so different at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's kinda hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:49.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Guess you kinda have to go there to really get it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.87,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.90,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,don't suppose…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.38,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You really think Princess Twilight would be okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know for sure that she wouldn't be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.36,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,That's not a particularly compelling argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.22,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She wants me to learn as much as I can about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:08.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And I'm not learning a whole lot just hanging out here in her castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:11.29,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:13.96,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I haven't ever seen you in that world, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:17.00,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,chances are you aren't gonna run into yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.12,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,…is something you don't hear everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:21.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,So, just lay low.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.61,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Don't draw too much attention to your…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.20,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You'll barely even notice I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.69,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Introducing you to my friends could be a nice distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But you'll also totally notice I'm there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:33.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and it will keep your mind off of other things that might be bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:39.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Can I go back with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.51,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's all pretty weird at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.11,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,but try to roll with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.15,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.61,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.37,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.87,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And what happened to the rest of my hoo…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.52,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Feet. Those are feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.43,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Remember the whole thing where I said you need to lay low?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.98,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Now would be a good time to play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.67,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.25,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You did say I'd make a good distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:37.62,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.28,Juniper,,0,0,0,,pick up this popcorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.03,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.43,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I command thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.33,Juniper,,0,0,0,,pick upeth this poppage of corn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.86,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Why won't this thing work anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.34,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Like…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,we were gonna eat some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:08:59.78,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.28,Juniper,,0,0,0,,make these annoying people go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.08,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Well, that kinda worked…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Juniper Montage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in the blazes are you doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Were you invited to the Daring Do premiere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:14.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No, crazy! No, concerning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No! Just no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.39,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wasn't invited to the premiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:25.47,Juniper,,0,0,0,,My uncle Canter Zoom felt bad for firing me, so he pulled some strings and got me this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:28.83,Juniper,,0,0,0,,As little as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:36.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Y'know, if you hadn't tried to sabotage the movie, you could be celebrating with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.53,Juniper,,0,0,0,,This should be my night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:42.72,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I would have found a way to be in the film if you all had stayed out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.85,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I would have been Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.14,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Everyone would've loved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.29,Juniper,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.15,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Can't you see what's right under your noses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.80,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd all just go away and leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.65,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Looks like I may be finally getting the hang of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.82,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Hi, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.97,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Six cell phones, all straight to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.14,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What's the worst that could have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:32.02,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Magic is on the loose here now, and it does not work the same way it does back in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.61,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Any number of terrible things could have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.83,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,And lately, I spend eighty percent of my time thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.95,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,My friends are probably fine. I'm overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.39,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,But maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.22,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't tell anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:51.02,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This is the problem you wanted to talk to Princess Twilight about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:54.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Because you can still talk it over with me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.76,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Or you could just journal with Princess Twilight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.81,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Whatever works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.11,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.89,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I know my friends and I have been given special powers for a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.82,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,and I want to be ready for whatever is gonna be thrown at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.87,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I guess knowing that is making me feel like I could never really relax and let my guard down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.23,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,so I end up obsessing about it and can't get out of my own head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That is a toughie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:23.97,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Guess my advice would be to just trust things will work themselves out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:27.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If you spend too much time worrying about the bad things that might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.14,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you'll miss out on all the good things that are happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:36.15,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Like how Princess Twilight's student is teaching me a lesson right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:37.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:38.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.23,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.76,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look around the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.32,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:50.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Any clue yet where we are or what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.93,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie's on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Nope, no wall over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Come out, come out, walls, wherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.95,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't get this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:09.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,There's no walls in here anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Somehow, some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:18.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,that dang Juniper sucked us all inside of that mirror of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or into some kind of limbo behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think I might be freaking out a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You call that a freakout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a deep-down-inside freakout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,On the upside, there's popcorn in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Mm, sticky…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How could this happen on the evening of my very first movie premiere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of all the nights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Curse you, cruel fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not our number-one problem right now, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But perhaps we can agree it's in the top five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is there really no way out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, my heavens! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Chocolate-covered almonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:06.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Dibs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.29,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's Juniper Montage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.28,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:20.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.92,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,She's trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.74,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,That's Fluttershy's barrette.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.63,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Wait here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.04,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.08,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you'd show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.95,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.88,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.69,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.05,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I'll never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.90,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:54.53,MrZoom,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I offered to get you this job after the stunt you pulled on my set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:56.97,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be Daring Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.31,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I just wanted people to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.25,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Everyone would love me if it weren't for you girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.94,Juniper,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.63,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd all just go away and leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.19,Juniper,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.58,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I know you want people to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.91,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,But trust me, the magic in that mirror is only gonna make things worse for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:23.06,Juniper,,0,0,0,,You're just saying that because you want the mirror for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.42,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,What I want is my friends back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:26.59,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Please, Juniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.03,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,You wished them into that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.86,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a way you can wish them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.45,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Or maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.68,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:01.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hooray! We're all together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:08.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If we're all together, then nobody out there knows where we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.24,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.08,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:18.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You mean Twilight's student back in Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,How would she know where…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You didn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She isn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.59,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I kinda told her she could come back here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:29.59,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You really think Princess Twilight would be okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know for sure that she wouldn't be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.97,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So sorry to interrupt, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Check out our geodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That's what I was trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Something's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This wasn't happening before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.85,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because all seven of us are together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is this a good thing or a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm going with not a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.85,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Now everyone will recognize I'm a real star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.06,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,first things first,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I need to get that mirror away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.26,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Want Mommy to take our picture together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.45,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,The mirror is breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If Starlight Glimmer doesn't find a way to get us out of here soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.55,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer, I hope you know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.74,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:38.74,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.37,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This mirror is nothing but trouble. You have to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:47.50,Juniper,,0,0,0,,What I realize is that you are just like those other girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.65,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:58.18,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can't make that wish unless you're the one holding the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I wish Sunset Shimmer and her friends would come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:20.19,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can't use it, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.40,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But my friends are trapped in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's dance magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:40.19,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Your friends stole my one chance at being famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Once you have it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Let your body move,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Step into the mu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.63,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Is fame really what you're after or…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,are you looking for something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.51,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Like…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.00,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Who would want to be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.85,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Because I understand you, Juniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:18.13,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You think getting revenge is going to make you feel better, but it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.22,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.49,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,don't make a mistake that you'll end up regretting for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.78,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I've already made too many mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.93,Juniper,,0,0,0,,What I've done is… is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.56,Juniper,,0,0,0,,unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:29.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No, Juniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.81,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know they'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:32.83,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But first,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you have to set them free!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:47.77,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.55,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I wish I could make up for my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.47,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Starlight, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.81,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So much for laying low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.83,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I think even Princess Twilight would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.53,Juniper,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.09,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.76,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,We've all been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.24,Juniper,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Manipulated an entire town into giving up their talents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.85,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,so they wouldn't think they were special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:34.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Overpowered by a magic I couldn't control and created a rift between two worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,almost destroying both of them in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.57,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Turned an entire school into my own personal zombie army
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.84,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,in hopes of conquering a distant pony world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wow! We are a really forgiving group!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.56,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm so sad to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I haven't really had the chance to get to know all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.34,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't have to leave yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.87,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Dear Sunset,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.39,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,some lessons are better learned in action,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.35,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,and you girls are great teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.07,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Starlight should stay for a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.25,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the premiere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Think you can focus on the positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.69,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:24.76,SunsetShimmer,,0,0,0,,I've just gotta live in the moment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:25.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONEC
